    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >绝赞的俯视角动作冒险游戏</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206060/extras/43e0aa1c9990fe5598605b4ee4442d76.poster.avif?t=1770123293\" width=584 height=410 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206060/extras/43e0aa1c9990fe5598605b4ee4442d76.webm?t=1770123293\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206060/extras/43e0aa1c9990fe5598605b4ee4442d76.mp4?t=1770123293\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >探索地图</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >清除地图上的障碍物，将地图连通起来</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >收集散布在关卡中的“努奴”，达到一定数量后可以清除障碍物</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206060/extras/328be0ac249f8e289b908c31592e292e.poster.avif?t=1770123293\" width=558 height=414 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206060/extras/328be0ac249f8e289b908c31592e292e.webm?t=1770123293\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206060/extras/328be0ac249f8e289b908c31592e292e.mp4?t=1770123293\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >打败敌人</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >用小车撞击敌人！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206060/extras/aed702c6e1599979fac8e99bfdaa3a40.poster.avif?t=1770123293\" width=570 height=420 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206060/extras/aed702c6e1599979fac8e99bfdaa3a40.webm?t=1770123293\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206060/extras/aed702c6e1599979fac8e99bfdaa3a40.mp4?t=1770123293\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >收集素材</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >寻找隐藏的收集要素</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >有的“努奴”非常隐蔽</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206060/extras/16237976f7a0519229f6cbef9985d05e.poster.avif?t=1770123293\" width=570 height=424 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206060/extras/16237976f7a0519229f6cbef9985d05e.webm?t=1770123293\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206060/extras/16237976f7a0519229f6cbef9985d05e.mp4?t=1770123293\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >建设据点（尚在开发中）</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用探险中获得的资源建设营地，解锁设施</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206060/extras/ff5243868ff3e203630b875641b6a0c6.poster.avif?t=1770123293\" width=764 height=426 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206060/extras/ff5243868ff3e203630b875641b6a0c6.webm?t=1770123293\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206060/extras/ff5243868ff3e203630b875641b6a0c6.mp4?t=1770123293\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >小鼠开车大冒险！</h2>",
